title: "Chill and Full Unbond in [pallet_staking]"

doc:
  - audience: Runtime Dev
    description: |
      Introduces a new `full_unbond` extrinsic to forcefully chill and unbond the full value
      bonded

      It also modifies the `unbond` extrinsic by forcefully chilling and unbonding the full value
      if the value to be unbonded is the total of what is bonded

crates:
  - name: pallet-staking
